Spring
====

1. web.xml

```
<servlet>
    <servlet-name>springweb</servlet-name>
    <servlet-class>org.springframework.web.servlet.DispatcherServlet</servlet-class>    
</servlet> 
``` 
will load beans in springweb-servlet.xml for servlet context.

```
<context-param>
  <param-name>contextConfigLocation</param-name>
  <param-value>/WEB-INF/spring/root-config.xml</param-value>
</context-param>
````
will load beans in root-config.xml for root application context. `ContextLoaderListener` is required.

```
<listener>
    <listener-class>org.springframework.web.context.ContextLoaderListener</listener-class>
</listener>
````
will load beans in applicationContext.xml for root application context by default.
